$ SQL*Plus: DESCRIBE
@ describe

`describe` shows basic(!) characteristics of
→ development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables[tables],
→ development/databases/Oracle/objects/views[views], object types or
→ development/databases/Oracle/PL-SQL[PL/SQL] objects.

{ Influencing appearance
  
  SQL*Plus settings that influence the output of `describe` are
    • `set linesize`
    • `set describe depth …`
    • `set describe ndent …`
    • `set describe line …`


}

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus
